          "description": "Write this module's current uniform values into the shared uniform buffer at byteOffset. Layout must match the field declarations returned by wgsl (in the same order). Receives the current frame dt (seconds). Modules tracking accumulated time (e.g. noise/turbulence) should advance their internal counter here to stay in sync when running in GPU mode (where apply is not called). Required when wgsl declares uniforms. Called every frame by the system before dispatching compute."
